name: Guardian Prime: Forest Sentinel
text: Guardian Prime emerged, gleaming under moonlight. Where the Cybernetic Enchanted Forest Guardian once tread, Prime stood taller, its cannons humming with potential. Its tail flickered with data streams, commanding the woods' magic-tech fusion. The forest's heart beat through it—a protector evolved, a sentinel reborn.
